data.description: Step right out of the pages of House Beautiful! This custom 3 bed, 3 1/2 bath home w/master suites both downstairs & up is full of thoughtful touches! Hardwood floors, extensive crown molding, recessed can lighting and TONS of windows are found throughout the home. Turn the lights down low & relax in front of the fire. Relax with a cup of coffee or glass of wine while enjoying striking views of Lake Cameron & mature trees from your two story front porch. Both upstairs bedrooms open out onto an upper porch with views of Lake Cameron. The house flows beautifully from front porch through its open living areas to your back deck fenced yard and park beyond.  The kitchen has easy access to all inside and outside living areas. Enjoy the peace & quiet of your back yard & neighboring ramble from the privacy of your rear deck.  There is just enough fenced back yard for gardening, pets or children. Generous storage areas inside & out. Energy efficiency features include foam insulation, tankless water heater, NEST thermostats & high efficiency heat pump. Energy bills available upon request. A 2 bay carport with 3rd parking space allows for convenient golf cart parking and charging. The exterior was painted in 2023.  Zoned controller for watering plants and pots on the porches, front and back yards.  Just a block from almost everything in the heart of The Waters, this house is a do not miss opportunity!
